summary: 2020 COACHMEN MIRANDA 35OS. CONSUMER WRITES IN REGARDS TO MISSING SCREW DOWN THE LINER OF SLIDE ENTRY DOOR. *LD    THE CONSUMER STATED THE VEHICLE EXPERIENCED MULTIPLE STRUCTURAL ISSUES. THE ENTRY DOOR NOT CLOSING PROPERLY AND THE KITCHEN SLIDE NOT GOING IN CORRECTLY ARE A SAFETY HAZARD. THE CONSUMER STATED THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO THE DEALER WHO, UNSUCCESSFULY, ATTEMPTED TO REPAIR THE FAILURES. THE VIN IS REGISTERING AS A VEHICLE OF A DIFFERENT MAKE, MODEL, AND MODEL YEAR. *JS
